Package: cadaver-ssl
Version: 0.19.1
Revision: 12
Maintainer: Ben Hines <bhines@alumni.ucsd.edu> 
Depends: libxml2-shlibs, readline-shlibs (>= 4.3-5), neon-ssl
BuildDepends: libxml2, readline (>= 4.3-5), neon-ssl, expat, tcltk-dev
Source: http://www.webdav.org/cadaver/cadaver-%v.tar.gz
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%i/share/man --bindir=%i/bin --with-libxml2
SetCFLAGS: -I%p/include/libxml2/libxml -no-cpp-precomp
NoSetLDFLAGS: true
GCC: 3.1
CompileScript:  <<
./configure %c
make
<<
InstallScript: <<
make install
strip %i/bin/cadaver
<<
DocFiles: README COPYING NEWS THANKS TODO ChangeLog FAQ INSTALL INTEROP
Description: WebDAV client.
DescDetail: <<
WebDAV client which supports file upload, download, on-screen display,
namespace operations (move/copy), collection creation and deletion, 
and locking operations.
<<
DescUsage: <<
Useful for speedy CLI idisk access and scripting. Use "cadaver http://idisk.mac.com/yourusername"
<<
DescPackaging: <<
Depends on neon-ssl 1.8. (19 does not work) I could not get it
to enable i18n and work properly. (it's disabled by default in the src)
<<
Homepage: http://www.webdav.org/cadaver
